{"tid":621191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度人好nice ! 愛爾蘭背包客遭姦殺　兇手把她毀容圖滅跡","createTime":"2018-04-08T06:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T13:52:57.000Z","uid":72009,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8554ab995b2e8c2b682f7be9ececd9f9af35ba88","tid":621191,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T06:18:09.000Z","msg":"28歲的麥可洛琳，去年3月被發現滿身鮮血、赤裸倒斃在果阿一塊農田上。警方經調查後證實死者身份，並從監視影像發現她死前曾與一名印度男子巴格茲(Vikat Bhagat)一起。<br />\n案情指出，麥可洛琳曾到過印度，因而認識巴格茲。嫌犯在一個偏僻地區企圖性侵麥克勞克林，她反抗，嫌犯就用啤酒瓶打她的頭，繼而把她性侵勒斃。為了毀屍滅跡，更用石塊把麥可洛琳的臉部打爛。<br />\n巴格茲在警方盤問下承認殺人，但他在庭上卻否認謀殺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180408/640_97621f34514ff42af5f5f166244e2747.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180408%2F640_97621f34514ff42af5f5f166244e2747.jpg&h=85d237b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180408/640_62d6b8e03a1c6a8f2476fd4d297ef835.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180408%2F640_62d6b8e03a1c6a8f2476fd4d297ef835.jpg&h=1ef5f20a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6160e67cbcdebc257a076329fe4496504c94def","tid":621191,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T06:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f504e38d2dfde2aad6eebe7a1b13ffe9f4320e6","tid":621191,"uid":179374,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T06:20:02.000Z","msg":"屌呢啲垃圾國家真係要滅國先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15269b183bf64bd47b2ad55b2a592165ec7b9a9c","tid":621191,"uid":165187,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T06:20:20.000Z","msg":"incredible India. fuck yeah<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" clas